Class BranchFlowControlImpl

    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, BranchFlowControl, IAclfAdjustment, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PSXfrPControlImpl, TapControlImpl

    public class BranchFlowControlImpl
extends NameTagImpl
implements BranchFlowControl
    An implementation of the model object 'Flow Control'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Parent Branch
    • Flow Control Type
    • Control Limit
    • Control On From Side
    • Control Spec
    • Control Range
    • Flow From2 To
    • Metered On From Side
